Hey there Carson fans! It's me! I have great news! Last week someone spoke to foster mom and asked to meet me. I loved them immediately!! They are cat lovers and have a CH kitty like me! They brought me home Thursday night and so far I'm doing great. I fall down more than my new sister who is like me but they will help me learn the house and make adjustments as needed. I'm so excited to start enjoying my new parents! ğŸ’œ

Thanks to all of you for your love and support since I was surrendered last month. Thanks for sharing my videos and spreading the word about Cerebellar Hypoplasia cats like me! ğŸˆ
Special thanks to my foster parents for taking me in so I was comfortable until I met my furrever parents ğŸ’•
Thanks to Willingboro Veterinary Clinic for making me part of the Grand Paws Club even though I insisted I was a young kitten who didn't need bloodwork! ğŸ˜‰

Unwanted litters are surrendered to us and then transferred to a placement partner for the chance at #adoption!
